<lb n="0365b28"/>堅固佛　南無<note n="0365010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">懷＝悅【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="0365010"><lem>懷</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【宮】" resp="Taisho">悅</rdg></app>解脫佛　南無無憂<note n="0365011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">疾＝度【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="0365011"><lem>疾</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【宮】" resp="Taisho">度</rdg></app>佛
<lb n="0365b29"/>　南無普見事見佛　南無大乘<note n="0365012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">道＝導【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="0365012"><lem>道</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【宮】" resp="Taisho">導</rdg></app>佛　南無
<pb ed="T" id="T14.0446a.0365c" n="0365c"/>
