<lb n="0365c19"/><p>一百佛<note place="inline"><note n="0365014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">過去＝竟【宋】【元】【宮】＊</note><app n="0365014"><lem>過去</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【宮】" resp="Taisho">竟</rdg></app></note></p>
